1
00:01:32,330 --> 00:01:39,990
[Better Halves]

2
00:01:40,210 --> 00:01:42,840
[Episode 19]

3
00:01:43,470 --> 00:01:45,250
Steamed buns! Hot steamed buns!

4
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:46,570
[Qingfeng Inn]

5
00:01:46,070 --> 00:01:47,870
Hot steamed buns!

6
00:01:51,430 --> 00:01:52,460
Young Master,

7
00:01:52,479 --> 00:01:53,880
your room payment is due.

8
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,840
Please wait a moment.

9
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:04,520
Sir, please bear with me
for a few more days.

10
00:02:04,580 --> 00:02:05,430
I'll find a way soon.

11
00:02:05,430 --> 00:02:07,230
Please do so as soon as possible.

12
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:22,640
Mr. Yan, look!

13
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,040
This is so beautiful.

14
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:26,630
It'll look great on you.

15
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,310
Boss,

16
00:02:30,329 --> 00:02:32,260
please pack this one,
this one, and this one

17
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:32,820
for me.

18
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:33,560
Sure.

19
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:38,520
What's wrong?

20
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,520
Why the long face all day?

21
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:42,329
Something troubling you?

22
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,050
Ke.

23
00:02:46,210 --> 00:02:47,810
Could you lend me some money?

24
00:02:48,100 --> 00:02:49,500
I left in such a hurry,

25
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:51,360
and there's so much to eat and see here
in the capital.

26
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,900
I spent all my travel money
without even realizing it.

27
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:55,100
That's it?

28
00:02:55,510 --> 00:02:56,170
No problem.

29
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,400
However,

30
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,640
this is all I have left today.

31
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:05,770
Take it for now.

32
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:07,360
Here.

33
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,210
Thank you, Ke.

34
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:13,140
It's just that after all this time,

35
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:14,850
there's still no sign of Mr. Lin Yuan.

36
00:03:14,850 --> 00:03:16,500
Searching like this is like
looking for a needle in a haystack,

37
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:18,560
and I don't know how long it will take.

38
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:21,710
Everything in the capital costs money -
food, clothes, lodging, transportation.

39
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:24,120
I don't know how long
this money will last.

40
00:03:24,370 --> 00:03:25,390
That's easy.

41
00:03:25,890 --> 00:03:27,100
Just check out of the inn

42
00:03:27,100 --> 00:03:28,070
and come stay at my place.

43
00:03:28,070 --> 00:03:30,130
That would save you a lot of expenses.

44
00:03:30,990 --> 00:03:33,160
Ke, you're truly saving me from disaster.

45
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,020
I will do everything in my power to repay

46
00:03:34,020 --> 00:03:36,020
the kindness you've shown me today.

47
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:38,240
But...

48
00:03:39,370 --> 00:03:41,329
Is there a problem?

49
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:43,540
There is indeed an unresolved issue.

50
00:03:43,870 --> 00:03:45,470
You're dressed as a man now,

51
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,900
and I'm still unmarried.

52
00:03:47,220 --> 00:03:48,050
If I

53
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:50,340
bring a strange man home to stay,

54
00:03:50,410 --> 00:03:53,010
my brothers and father
would tear the roof off.

55
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:54,150
Besides,

56
00:03:54,510 --> 00:03:55,750
if Brother Lu finds out

57
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:57,050
I brought a man home,

58
00:03:57,620 --> 00:03:59,440
I don't know what he would think.

59
00:04:00,590 --> 00:04:02,380
So that's what you're worried about.

60
00:04:02,380 --> 00:04:03,980
That's easy to fix. Let's go.

61
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,760
Mr. Yan.

62
00:04:27,780 --> 00:04:28,700
No.

63
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:32,720
Miss Yan, you look absolutely stunning
in this outfit.

64
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:34,140
It's fine now, right?

65
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,250
Of course it is.

66
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:39,080
Dear, it's my turn now.

67
00:04:39,860 --> 00:04:41,320
Father, Mother, I'm back.

68
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,470
Ke.

69
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,300
Ke.

70
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:47,650
And who is this young lady?

71
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,200
Let me introduce her to everyone.

72
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:50,640
This is my new friend,

73
00:04:50,659 --> 00:04:51,470
Yan Qiyue.

74
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,420
Greetings, Uncle and Aunt.

75
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:54,680
Greetings, everyone.

76
00:04:55,050 --> 00:04:57,320
Qiyue, this is my eldest brother,
Shi Xianxian,

77
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,530
my second brother, Shi Chongshan,

78
00:04:58,530 --> 00:05:00,390
and my little cousin, Shi Qin'er.

79
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:01,950
Nice to meet you, Miss Qiyue.

80
00:05:01,950 --> 00:05:03,480
So you're Cousin's friend.

81
00:05:03,510 --> 00:05:05,170
Miss Qiyue, you're so pretty.

82
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:07,050
Greetings Eldest Brother, Second Brother,

83
00:05:07,050 --> 00:05:08,330
and hello to you, Qin'er.

84
00:05:08,330 --> 00:05:10,300
Where are you from, Miss Qiyue?

85
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:13,880
I'm from out of town.

86
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,010
From out of town.

87
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:18,470
Mother, she came to visit the capital.

88
00:05:18,610 --> 00:05:20,070
She has no relatives here.

89
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:22,410
I didn't feel at ease

90
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,560
letting such a pretty girl

91
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,760
wander around alone.

92
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:25,760
Mother.

93
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:29,010
Could she stay with us for a few days?

94
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:32,590
Since she's your friend,

95
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:34,810
she's certainly welcome in our home.

96
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,550
I'll tell the servants

97
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:38,560
to tidy up the room in the east wing.

98
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:39,860
You can stay there.

99
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,950
It's close to Ke's room,

100
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:42,590
so it'll be convenient for you two.

101
00:05:42,590 --> 00:05:44,659
Thank you so much, Uncle and Aunt.

102
00:05:45,050 --> 00:05:46,760
Sorry for imposing on you.

103
00:05:47,270 --> 00:05:48,200
It's no trouble.

104
00:05:48,490 --> 00:05:50,290
Just treat this as your own home.

105
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,240
Besides Ke,

106
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:53,270
you can also ask these two for help
if you need anything.

107
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,070
That's right, Miss Qiyue.

108
00:05:54,070 --> 00:05:56,000
Feel free to come to us for anything.

109
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,510
Miss Qiyue is Ke's friend,

110
00:05:57,540 --> 00:05:59,040
which makes you a friend of our family.

111
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,690
Please don't stand on ceremony.

112
00:06:00,690 --> 00:06:02,510
Thank you, Eldest Brother
and Second Brother.

113
00:06:02,510 --> 00:06:04,040
Come, I'll show you around.

114
00:06:05,310 --> 00:06:06,080
Go on, go on.

115
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:07,440
Let's go.

116
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,380
Master.

117
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:19,690
Master.

118
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,600
Reporting to Master.

119
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:24,030
Miss Shi didn't meet Mr. Yan today.

120
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:27,430
But, she brought

121
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:29,270
a young and beautiful lady home today.

122
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:30,180
A young lady?

123
00:06:34,210 --> 00:06:36,090
Ke has been quite active lately.

124
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:41,620
Ms. Li,

125
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,960
the two Shi brothers

126
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:46,480
seem quite interested in that young

127
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:47,640
and beautiful lady.

128
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:57,030
Why are you telling me

129
00:06:57,230 --> 00:06:58,920
about this?

130
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:02,290
What does it have to do with me?

131
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:06,470
It doesn't have anything to do with you?

132
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:09,360
That young lady is getting close

133
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,940
with the whole Shi family.

134
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:14,520
Does it really have nothing
to do with you?

135
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:30,190
These new fabrics that just arrived
are all pretty good in quality.

136
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:31,630
Sort them out later

137
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:32,710
and put them away.

138
00:07:32,710 --> 00:07:33,560
Okay.

139
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:34,130
Alright.

140
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,920
Ms. Li, how have you been lately?

141
00:07:40,630 --> 00:07:43,030
Mr. Shi, are you here to buy something?

142
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:44,350
Yes,

143
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,430
you reminded me, I almost forgot.

144
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:47,680
I'm here to purchase some items.

145
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,610
Ms. Li, please go on with your work.

146
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:53,270
Would you like to buy some rouge,
Young Master?

147
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:54,430
This is rouge, right?

148
00:07:54,430 --> 00:07:54,870
Yes.

149
00:07:54,870 --> 00:07:56,270
Which one sells the best?

150
00:07:56,340 --> 00:07:58,800
This one
is more popular among young ladies.

151
00:07:59,030 --> 00:08:00,950
Good, Miss Qiyue will definitely like it.

152
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:01,360
Wrap it up.

153
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:01,890
Alright.

154
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:06,610
This one too,

155
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,800
wrap this up as well.

156
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,460
Certainly.

157
00:08:08,670 --> 00:08:11,180
What else do young ladies like?

158
00:08:11,210 --> 00:08:13,810
You might want to look at these
round fans here.

159
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,310
Alright. This one,

160
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,140
wrap this up too.

161
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:18,770
Alright.

162
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:20,950
Miss Qiyue will definitely like it.

163
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:24,640
Who told you to put this here?

164
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:25,900
Does it look good here?

165
00:08:26,270 --> 00:08:28,630
In the future, do not do things
I didn't order you to do.

166
00:08:28,630 --> 00:08:29,240
Yes.

167
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:31,000
Take it away now!

168
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:35,370
Making decisions all by yourself.

169
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:38,750
Sister Pan'er, why are you upset?

170
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:41,080
Is something bothering you lately?

171
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:42,799
Ke, you're here.

172
00:08:43,380 --> 00:08:45,910
Chief has lost
quite a bit of weight recently.

173
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:49,540
Are you two dieting together?

174
00:08:52,590 --> 00:08:55,250
Pan'er, are things with my Eldest Brother
going well lately?

175
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:56,180
Well? Not at all!

176
00:08:57,130 --> 00:08:58,790
His heart isn't with me at all.

177
00:09:00,730 --> 00:09:01,790
That's impossible.

178
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:03,320
My brother isn't like that.

179
00:09:05,340 --> 00:09:06,940
Sister Pan'er, don't worry.

180
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,480
Leave it to me.

181
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:09,660
I'll figure something out.

182
00:09:09,660 --> 00:09:12,810
Ke, weren't you here to see Chief?

183
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,990
I'll come back tomorrow.

184
00:09:13,990 --> 00:09:14,630
Goodbye!

185
00:09:29,050 --> 00:09:29,760
Eldest Brother!

186
00:09:29,690 --> 00:09:32,590
[Yachun House]

187
00:09:30,890 --> 00:09:33,150
Eldest Brother, you're back.

188
00:09:33,710 --> 00:09:34,770
Come, quickly.

189
00:09:36,820 --> 00:09:38,270
Ke, what's the matter?

190
00:09:38,970 --> 00:09:39,900
Eldest Brother.

191
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:42,360
Have you been to Xibao Pavilion recently?

192
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:43,440
Yes.

193
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,910
Didn't you ask me
to get some daily necessities

194
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,000
for Miss Qiyue?

195
00:09:48,430 --> 00:09:50,020
Did you notice

196
00:09:50,170 --> 00:09:52,300
anything unusual with Sister Pan'er?

197
00:09:52,860 --> 00:09:53,640
Unusual?

198
00:09:54,740 --> 00:09:55,460
Not at all.

199
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:57,480
She's still as

200
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:00,070
beautiful as always.

201
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,770
Eldest Brother.

202
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,750
Have you thought about

203
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,560
your future plans together?

204
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,850
Ke, what are you talking about?

205
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,790
What future? What plans?

206
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:15,180
She's the boss of Xibao Pavilion,

207
00:10:15,980 --> 00:10:19,110
and I'm just a lowly constable.

208
00:10:19,530 --> 00:10:22,220
Eldest Brother, how can you say that?

209
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,570
The Shi family may not be prestigious,

210
00:10:24,570 --> 00:10:26,070
but we're still a respectable family.

211
00:10:26,070 --> 00:10:28,200
You're the eldest son of the family, too.

212
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:30,510
You're not inferior to those
rich young masters at all.

213
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:31,830
And you're honest,

214
00:10:31,850 --> 00:10:32,940
considerate, and family-oriented.

215
00:10:32,940 --> 00:10:35,400
You're the ideal type
for many young ladies.

216
00:10:35,630 --> 00:10:36,450
Really?

217
00:10:36,470 --> 00:10:37,200
Of course.

218
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:40,580
I'm not as good as you say.

219
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:45,440
Eldest Brother,
you need to be more confident.

220
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:47,680
Even if what you say is true,

221
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:51,030
Ms. Li is beautiful, smart, and capable.

222
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:54,170
She's so perfect. I'm not worthy of her.

223
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:58,030
Alright, Ke.

224
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,810
I'm going to my room now.

225
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,200
You get some rest too.

226
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:03,570
Eldest Brother!

227
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,520
It's so frustrating.

228
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:13,150
Eldest Brother and Sister Pan'er
clearly have feelings for each other,

229
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:15,080
yet he is so lacking in confidence.

230
00:11:16,630 --> 00:11:17,430
This won't do.

231
00:11:18,380 --> 00:11:20,600
I need to find a way to help him.

232
00:11:22,990 --> 00:11:24,880
[Fourth Archway]

233
00:11:24,990 --> 00:11:27,160
[Wang's Wonton]

234
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,010
Ms. Li!

235
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:56,920
Don't look back.

236
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,010
Ms. Li!

237
00:12:02,690 --> 00:12:03,730
Ms. Li!

238
00:12:06,330 --> 00:12:07,300
Ms. Li.

239
00:12:08,550 --> 00:12:11,010
Why is she holding
that young master's hand?

240
00:12:16,270 --> 00:12:16,950
Let's go.

241
00:12:20,780 --> 00:12:22,220
[Shi's Ancestral Hall]

242
00:12:29,780 --> 00:12:32,760
[Reverence in Silence and Stillness]

243
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:39,770
Eldest Brother.

244
00:12:42,070 --> 00:12:45,030
[Reverence in Silence and Stillness]

245
00:12:43,850 --> 00:12:45,450
Something's bothering you?

246
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:48,560
No.

247
00:12:50,420 --> 00:12:51,950
I'm just admiring the moon.

248
00:12:52,290 --> 00:12:53,790
The moon looks nice tonight.

249
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:55,030
[Reverence in Silence and Stillness]

250
00:12:56,870 --> 00:12:59,000
What's so nice about this waning moon?

251
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:05,370
You don't seem very happy.

252
00:13:08,990 --> 00:13:10,970
I-I-I'm not unhappy.

253
00:13:12,870 --> 00:13:14,290
I'm going to bed now.

254
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:16,360
Ke, you should get some rest too.

255
00:13:19,170 --> 00:13:28,040
[Reverence in Silence and Stillness]

256
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:31,960
Ke.

257
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,360
What's wrong?

258
00:13:36,390 --> 00:13:39,180
I might have messed something up.

259
00:13:39,300 --> 00:13:42,060
I originally wanted to use Mr. Yan
to motivate my Eldest Brother,

260
00:13:42,060 --> 00:13:44,590
but I didn't expect him to become
so dejected.

261
00:13:44,690 --> 00:13:46,250
How can I help my Eldest Brother

262
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:47,590
get Sister Pan'er back?

263
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:49,200
When it comes to matters of the heart,

264
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:51,250
what matters is mutual understanding
between two people.

265
00:13:51,250 --> 00:13:53,270
You need to encourage your brother
to express what's in his heart,

266
00:13:53,270 --> 00:13:56,360
to communicate his feelings
in the most straightforward way,

267
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:58,030
so they don't keep
second-guessing each other

268
00:13:58,030 --> 00:14:00,030
and end up uncertain about
each other's true feelings.

269
00:14:00,030 --> 00:14:01,490
You're right, Brother Lu.

270
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:03,930
I didn't expect Mr. Yan
to have such an effect.

271
00:14:03,930 --> 00:14:05,870
My brother doesn't know how to handle it.

272
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:08,440
I'll need to guide him more.

273
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:17,160
I hear you've been getting close to
Mr. Yan lately.

274
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:23,280
Are you jealous?

275
00:14:24,370 --> 00:14:26,370
Mr. Yan and I are truly just friends.

276
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:26,850
Really.

277
00:14:26,970 --> 00:14:29,260
♪ I write a song of spring breeze
in your dream ♪

278
