552
00:28:35,410 --> 00:28:36,470
Everyone heard that, right?

553
00:28:36,470 --> 00:28:38,030
He admitted it was a bank note.

554
00:28:38,030 --> 00:28:39,880
Somehow, it turned into
blank paper in my hands.

555
00:28:39,880 --> 00:28:41,120
I don't care, give me back my bank note!

556
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:42,270
How could it turn into blank paper?

557
00:28:42,270 --> 00:28:43,600
Return my bank note now!

558
00:28:44,360 --> 00:28:45,640
Is this some kind of magic trick?

559
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:47,000
Heaven help me.

560
00:28:47,270 --> 00:28:48,120
The bank note

561
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:49,830
was meant to save

562
00:28:49,860 --> 00:28:51,330
my 80-year-old mother!

563
00:28:51,350 --> 00:28:52,720
How could I possibly use this money

564
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:54,090
to scam people?

565
00:28:54,120 --> 00:28:55,000
Young Master,

566
00:28:55,150 --> 00:28:56,000
if you really took his bank note,

567
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:57,480
just return it to him.

568
00:28:57,510 --> 00:28:59,440
I said I didn't take it, so I didn't.

569
00:29:00,230 --> 00:29:02,070
Let's go see a magistrate now,

570
00:29:02,090 --> 00:29:03,600
and settle this in court.

571
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:04,280
Let's go.

572
00:29:04,920 --> 00:29:05,980
What are you doing?

573
00:29:07,100 --> 00:29:08,080
I won't go!

574
00:29:08,100 --> 00:29:09,250
I-I-I won't go!

575
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:11,120
Common people like me,

576
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:12,790
with no power or influence,

577
00:29:12,790 --> 00:29:13,490
if I go in,

578
00:29:13,790 --> 00:29:14,920
will I ever come out?

579
00:29:15,590 --> 00:29:17,740
My poor 80-year-old mother.

580
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:20,580
Mother, your child has failed you!

581
00:29:20,600 --> 00:29:22,730
I don't have money for your treatment.

582
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:23,830
Alright.

583
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:27,530
If your mother is truly ill,

584
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:29,530
take this money for now.

585
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:31,440
Wait.

586
00:29:39,900 --> 00:29:41,510
Do you remember which bank

587
00:29:41,540 --> 00:29:42,750
issued the note?

588
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:45,470
It was Jiaotai Bank.

589
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,730
Good that you remember.

590
00:29:47,730 --> 00:29:49,830
Now, let's go to the magistrate's office
together

591
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:51,160
to seek justice for you,

592
00:29:51,250 --> 00:29:53,450
and then visit the bank to investigate.

593
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:56,440
I-I-I was mistaken,

594
00:29:56,810 --> 00:29:58,600
it was from an out-of-town bank.

595
00:29:58,600 --> 00:30:00,360
No matter which bank it's from,

596
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:02,750
going to the authorities
is the most appropriate action.

597
00:30:02,750 --> 00:30:04,650
An ordinary person with a bank note

598
00:30:04,650 --> 00:30:05,750
would treasure it dearly,

599
00:30:05,750 --> 00:30:06,610
yet somehow you

600
00:30:06,910 --> 00:30:09,240
can't even remember which bank issued it,

601
00:30:09,410 --> 00:30:11,640
and you're afraid to go to
the authorities.

602
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:13,440
You must have something to hide.

603
00:30:22,570 --> 00:30:23,480
Everyone, look here.

604
00:30:22,990 --> 00:30:24,650
[Inn]

605
00:30:23,520 --> 00:30:25,240
There's a hidden layer
in this blank paper.

606
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:26,880
The bank note was drawn on it.

607
00:30:27,650 --> 00:30:30,010
How could you do this at such a young age?

608
00:30:34,890 --> 00:30:38,600
Do you know the punishment for
forging documents?

609
00:30:39,320 --> 00:30:40,540
Give it back.

610
00:30:40,570 --> 00:30:41,830
You'll pay for this!

611
00:30:41,940 --> 00:30:43,430
Don't run!

612
00:30:47,890 --> 00:30:49,880
[Inn]

613
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:50,250
Thank you for your help, Miss.

614
00:30:50,250 --> 00:30:51,380
My surname is Huang.

615
00:30:51,590 --> 00:30:53,360
May I ask your name, Miss?

616
00:30:53,470 --> 00:30:54,650
You're too kind, Mr. Huang.

617
00:30:54,650 --> 00:30:55,710
I am Yan Qiyue.

618
00:30:56,170 --> 00:30:58,100
It's not easy being away from home.

619
00:30:58,460 --> 00:31:00,220
That person was really too much.

620
00:31:00,220 --> 00:31:02,550
I couldn't stand by and watch,
so I helped.

621
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:06,830
Put your money away.

622
00:31:09,790 --> 00:31:10,920
This matter is settled.

623
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:11,950
I'll take my leave now.

624
00:31:11,950 --> 00:31:12,960
[Inn]

625
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:14,570
Miss Qiyue.

626
00:31:16,890 --> 00:31:18,290
Forgive my boldness,

627
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:21,260
but I'd like to invite you
for a meal

628
00:31:21,290 --> 00:31:22,490
to show my gratitude.

629
00:31:22,490 --> 00:31:23,820
I just couldn't stand the injustice.

630
00:31:23,820 --> 00:31:26,080
You don't need to be so polite, Mr. Huang.

631
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:27,070
No.

632
00:31:27,350 --> 00:31:29,440
I'm truly grateful for your help today.

633
00:31:29,440 --> 00:31:31,920
Let's be friends.

634
00:31:32,760 --> 00:31:34,590
Alright, let's be friends.

635
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,520
Then may I invite you

636
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:38,490
to dine at Xibao Pavilion?

637
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:41,400
No wonder someone tried to extort him.

638
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:43,060
He's really a fool with money.

639
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:46,620
Doesn't he know how much it costs

640
00:31:46,650 --> 00:31:48,050
to eat at Xibao Pavilion?

641
00:31:50,110 --> 00:31:51,790
Never mind, just follow me.

642
00:31:57,570 --> 00:32:05,750
[Noodle Soup]

643
00:31:58,600 --> 00:32:00,260
We're here. This is the place.

644
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:03,030
This is my and my friend's
favorite noodle stall.

645
00:32:03,090 --> 00:32:04,860
Boss, two bowls of beef noodles, please.

646
00:32:04,860 --> 00:32:06,590
Alright, please wait a moment.

647
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:08,830
The beef noodles here
are tender and smooth.

648
00:32:08,830 --> 00:32:09,690
They melt in your mouth,

649
00:32:09,690 --> 00:32:12,420
You can't find anything like this
anywhere else.

650
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:14,690
I offered to take her to Xibao Pavilion,

651
00:32:14,690 --> 00:32:17,340
but she brought me
to this small stall instead,

652
00:32:17,550 --> 00:32:19,440
and she seems so familiar with this place.

653
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,830
Seems she's a frugal girl

654
00:32:20,830 --> 00:32:22,230
from an ordinary family.

655
00:32:23,180 --> 00:32:23,870
Have a seat.

656
00:32:25,310 --> 00:32:28,200
Alright, I'll give it a proper try then.

657
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:35,560
[Noodle Soup]

658
00:32:33,070 --> 00:32:35,090
Here are your noodles, folks!

659
00:32:38,180 --> 00:32:38,810
Thank you.

660
00:32:44,730 --> 00:32:45,560
Go ahead, eat.

661
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,660
Thank you.

662
00:32:57,410 --> 00:32:58,730
What a fruitless day.

663
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:03,130
When will I be able to meet Mr. Lin Yuan?

664
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:07,300
Miss Qiyue.

665
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:08,880
Miss Qiyue.

666
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:12,460
Why aren't you eating?

667
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:13,920
Something on your mind?

668
00:33:15,800 --> 00:33:16,810
Not really.

669
00:33:18,240 --> 00:33:20,200
Actually, if something's bothering you,

670
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:21,520
you can talk to me about it.

671
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:22,650
Maybe I can help you.

672
00:33:24,250 --> 00:33:25,870
The thing I'm thinking about

673
00:33:26,760 --> 00:33:27,960
is very complicated.

674
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:30,360
You can't help me with it.

675
00:33:31,270 --> 00:33:32,400
If you don't tell me,

676
00:33:32,430 --> 00:33:33,960
how do you know I can't help?

677
00:33:37,370 --> 00:33:38,570
I want to get married.

678
00:33:39,090 --> 00:33:41,320
G-G-Get married?

679
00:33:41,890 --> 00:33:44,010
See? I told you

680
00:33:44,030 --> 00:33:45,230
you can't help me.

681
00:33:46,350 --> 00:33:47,930
The person I like

682
00:33:48,360 --> 00:33:49,350
is like

683
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:51,120
a fleeting dream to me.

684
00:33:51,490 --> 00:33:52,840
I've never met him,

685
00:33:53,030 --> 00:33:54,740
don't even know where he is,

686
00:33:55,460 --> 00:33:56,880
but I just like him.

687
00:33:59,320 --> 00:34:00,480
This feeling

688
00:34:01,750 --> 00:34:03,680
must be hard to understand, right?

689
00:34:05,270 --> 00:34:06,070
I understand.

690
00:34:09,150 --> 00:34:11,409
Actually, the feeling of liking someone

691
00:34:11,409 --> 00:34:13,190
is probably the same for everyone.

692
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,199
But I think

693
00:34:14,219 --> 00:34:16,060
as long as you try your best to pursue it,

694
00:34:16,060 --> 00:34:18,120
even if it doesn't work out in the end,

695
00:34:18,389 --> 00:34:19,920
you won't have any regrets.

696
00:34:22,330 --> 00:34:23,300
That makes sense.

697
00:34:23,300 --> 00:34:25,500
Mr. Huang and I really do get along well.

698
00:34:25,880 --> 00:34:26,409
Here.

699
00:34:26,830 --> 00:34:28,800
Let me raise a cup to you
with tea instead of wine.

700
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:29,800
It's a pleasure to meet you.

701
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:31,020
I'm also very happy

702
00:34:31,260 --> 00:34:32,380
to meet Miss Qiyue.

703
00:34:40,550 --> 00:34:41,870
This is really delicious.

704
00:34:41,870 --> 00:34:42,429
Right?

705
00:34:43,500 --> 00:34:45,670
This was introduced
by a friend of mine, Shi Fa'ke,

706
00:34:45,670 --> 00:34:47,000
Ke, who brought me here.

707
00:34:47,659 --> 00:34:48,659
Is that so?

708
00:34:48,350 --> 00:34:56,530
[Shi's Mansion]

709
00:34:58,170 --> 00:34:59,780
Thank you for walking me back, Mr. Huang,

710
00:34:59,780 --> 00:35:01,360
You should go home and rest now.

711
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:04,040
I should be the one
thanking you, Miss Qiyue,

712
00:35:04,910 --> 00:35:06,590
Thank you for your help.

713
00:35:06,930 --> 00:35:08,790
No need to be so formal, Mr. Huang.

714
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:10,240
Miss Qiyue.

715
00:35:11,690 --> 00:35:13,980
When can we meet again?

716
00:35:14,810 --> 00:35:16,540
Let's make plans another time.

717
00:35:17,420 --> 00:35:20,200
Alright, then I'll take my leave.

718
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,320
Mr. Huang.

719
00:35:24,080 --> 00:35:27,170
Shall we go to the snack street next time?

720
00:35:27,510 --> 00:35:28,570
Snack street?

721
00:35:29,150 --> 00:35:31,360
-Okay. It's a...
-A promise.

722
00:35:36,380 --> 00:35:37,340
I'll go in now.

723
00:35:37,700 --> 00:35:38,440
Okay.

724
00:35:58,560 --> 00:35:59,870
Snack street.

725
00:36:09,310 --> 00:36:11,360
Ke, why aren't you sleeping yet?

726
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:14,080
Today, Chief Matchmaker Fang
received an imperial decree

727
00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:16,710
to escort the princess to a vassal state
for her marriage.

728
00:36:16,710 --> 00:36:18,110
To be as excellent as her,

729
00:36:18,230 --> 00:36:20,030
I still need to work much harder.

730
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:22,740
What's so enviable about escorting
a princess to marriage?

731
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:24,450
Did they ever
ask for the princess's opinion?

732
00:36:24,450 --> 00:36:25,910
A princess is a person too.

733
00:36:26,090 --> 00:36:28,550
Why can't she marry someone
she truly loves?

734
00:36:28,730 --> 00:36:30,190
They all speak of righteousness
and morality,

735
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:31,320
claiming to serve the country
and the people,

736
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:33,390
but they're really
just using the princess as a pawn,

737
00:36:33,390 --> 00:36:34,990
manipulating her however they please.

738
00:36:34,990 --> 00:36:37,080
What's up with you?

739
00:36:37,100 --> 00:36:38,430
Why are you so worked up?

740
00:36:41,950 --> 00:36:42,750
It's nothing.

741
00:36:44,150 --> 00:36:46,110
Are you in a bad mood?

742
00:36:46,510 --> 00:36:47,970
You can talk to me about it.

743
00:36:50,150 --> 00:36:52,210
I just haven't found Mr. Lin Yuan yet,

744
00:36:52,270 --> 00:36:53,260
and

745
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:55,160
I couldn't even get his new work.

746
00:36:55,630 --> 00:36:56,710
I'll help you.

747
00:36:57,150 --> 00:36:59,840
But I'm afraid that it'll all be in vain.

748
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:02,030
But...

749
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:06,120
Haven't you ever had an impossible dream?

750
00:37:07,230 --> 00:37:08,250
Of course I have.

751
00:37:08,920 --> 00:37:11,500
I was born into the family
of the no.1 matchmaker in the world.

752
00:37:11,500 --> 00:37:12,720
Since childhood, I believed that

753
00:37:12,720 --> 00:37:14,920
I would become the no.1 matchmaker too.

754
00:37:15,070 --> 00:37:16,290
But back then,

755
00:37:16,600 --> 00:37:19,270
I couldn't even complete
one matchmaking case per month.

756
00:37:19,270 --> 00:37:21,800
I could only think about
my little beggar boy.

757
00:37:22,090 --> 00:37:23,730
I wanted him to fulfill his promise

758
00:37:23,730 --> 00:37:24,860
so I could marry him.

759
00:37:25,470 --> 00:37:27,050
But I didn't even know his name

760
00:37:27,050 --> 00:37:28,390
or where he lived.

761
00:37:28,410 --> 00:37:29,370
What about now?

762
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:30,150
How is it now?

763
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:31,400
Now,

764
00:37:32,010 --> 00:37:33,730
I've become a real marriage broker,

765
00:37:33,730 --> 00:37:36,620
and I've also found my little boy.

766
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:40,690
Qiyue.

767
00:37:41,670 --> 00:37:43,090
I think I understand now.

768
00:37:43,350 --> 00:37:45,810
Things that everyone thinks are impossible

769
00:37:46,290 --> 00:37:47,840
seem to work out if you just persist

770
00:37:47,840 --> 00:37:49,040
a little longer.

771
00:37:50,150 --> 00:37:51,420
Do you really think so?

772
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:53,300
Ke, you truly understand me best.

773
00:37:53,510 --> 00:37:54,460
I know

774
00:37:54,680 --> 00:37:57,100
you won't be satisfied until you meet him.

775
00:37:57,590 --> 00:37:58,550
Don't worry,

776
00:37:58,630 --> 00:38:01,030
I'll definitely help you find
Mr. Lin Yuan.

777
00:38:01,960 --> 00:38:04,360
Ma'am, could you recommend
something delicious?

778
00:38:02,230 --> 00:38:04,290
[Yixiang Pawnshop]

779
00:38:04,440 --> 00:38:05,710
These are all delicious.

780
00:38:05,710 --> 00:38:06,670
This one sells the best,

781
00:38:06,670 --> 00:38:08,670
and this is a daily limited edition.

782
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:09,890
It looks beautiful.

783
00:38:10,190 --> 00:38:12,940
Yes, it's good for gifts or for yourself.

784
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:14,790
[Yixiang Pawnshop]

785
00:38:13,070 --> 00:38:14,230
But isn't it a bit expensive?

786
00:38:14,230 --> 00:38:15,510
This is limited edition.

787
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:17,360
My brother only makes 99 of these per day,

788
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:18,110
they're limited edition.

789
00:38:18,110 --> 00:38:18,910
Alright then.

790
00:38:19,720 --> 00:38:20,360
Let's go.

791
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:24,300
Take a look.

792
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:25,510
Take care.

793
00:38:25,510 --> 00:38:26,320
Ketian!

794
00:38:28,110 --> 00:38:29,280
Long time no see.

795
00:38:30,110 --> 00:38:31,440
What are you doing here?

796
00:38:33,950 --> 00:38:34,800
Ketian.

797
00:38:35,260 --> 00:38:37,580
Your words have broken my heart.

798
00:38:37,820 --> 00:38:40,010
We were once engaged.

799
00:38:40,110 --> 00:38:42,580
Why are you so cold to me now?

800
00:38:42,710 --> 00:38:43,310
Zhu Yizhi,

801
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:45,030
don't disturb my business here.

802
00:38:45,030 --> 00:38:45,890
What are you...

803
00:38:46,230 --> 00:38:47,290
What are you doing?

804
00:38:48,480 --> 00:38:49,680
Show some restraint.

805
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:53,390
Let go of me!

806
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:57,410
Well, I came here because

807
00:38:57,440 --> 00:38:59,230
I'm a bit short on cash lately.

808
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:02,940
I want you to take care of your old flame.

809
00:39:04,330 --> 00:39:05,190
You want money?

810
00:39:05,230 --> 00:39:05,810
Yes.

811
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:06,730
Why don't you just squat by the roadside

812
00:39:06,730 --> 00:39:08,020
with a bowl?

813
00:39:08,150 --> 00:39:09,480
Why come to He's Bakery?

814
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:13,420
Let me tell you, He Ketian,

815
00:39:13,680 --> 00:39:15,850
you're a daughter-in-law
of the Zhu family,

816
00:39:15,850 --> 00:39:17,800
so the He family's money is my money.

817
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:19,260
If you don't give me money,

818
00:39:20,590 --> 00:39:22,140
-I'll smash your shop
-What are you doing?

819
00:39:22,140 --> 00:39:23,440
so you won't
be able to do business anymore!

820
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:23,840
You...

821
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:25,510
Stop talking and hand over the money!

822
00:39:25,510 --> 00:39:26,730
Let go of me!

823
00:39:26,580 --> 00:39:31,120
[Abundant Wealth]

824
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:27,630
You're hurting me!

825
00:39:27,630 --> 00:39:28,230
Come here.

826
00:39:28,840 --> 00:39:30,900
Zhu Yizhi! You shameless scoundrel.

827
00:39:30,930 --> 00:39:32,110
I broke off our engagement long ago,

828
00:39:32,110 --> 00:39:33,840
yet you still dare to harass me.

829
00:39:35,460 --> 00:39:36,440
You dare push me?

830
00:39:37,030 --> 00:39:38,430
You want me to beat you up?

831
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:44,060
[Abundant Wealth]

832
00:39:40,990 --> 00:39:42,040
Give me the money!

833
00:39:43,120 --> 00:39:44,450
Are you giving it or not?

834
00:39:44,830 --> 00:39:45,150
Brother!

835
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:46,550
Ketian, are you alright?

836
00:39:48,440 --> 00:39:49,420
You bastard!

837
00:39:49,670 --> 00:39:52,220
If you cause any more trouble,
I'm calling the authorities!

838
00:39:52,220 --> 00:39:52,970
Go ahead and report me!

839
00:39:52,890 --> 00:39:55,140
[He's Bakery]

840
00:39:53,190 --> 00:39:54,110
I want to see if you can

841
00:39:54,110 --> 00:39:55,510
leave this shop today.

842
00:39:55,740 --> 00:39:56,270
Smash it!

843
00:39:56,280 --> 00:39:57,340
-Yes sir!
-Yes sir!

844
00:40:02,710 --> 00:40:03,430
Stop!

845
00:40:16,040 --> 00:40:18,210
How are we supposed to do business?

846
00:40:21,330 --> 00:40:22,130
Go report this to the authorities.

847
00:40:22,130 --> 00:40:23,130
Stop fighting!

848
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:24,610
Brother!

849
00:40:29,670 --> 00:40:30,880
Zhu Yizhi!

850
00:40:31,130 --> 00:40:33,430
[He's Bakery]

851
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:32,000
Brother!

852
00:40:32,430 --> 00:40:33,190
Brother!

853
00:40:33,340 --> 00:40:35,150
Are you okay? Are you hurt?

854
00:40:35,930 --> 00:40:36,900
Master, something terrible has happened!

855
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:38,420
Zhu Yizhi is causing a ruckus
at He's Bakery.

856
00:40:38,420 --> 00:40:40,080
He's destroying the shop right now.

857
00:40:40,080 --> 00:40:40,790
What?

858
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:44,500
Don't you dare hit my brother!

859
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:45,500
Get out of the way!

860
00:40:46,510 --> 00:40:47,100
Ketian!

861
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:48,370
Second Brother!

862
00:40:50,180 --> 00:40:51,750
What's going on here?

863
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:55,190
You again.

864
00:40:55,630 --> 00:40:56,630
I've long suspected

865
00:40:56,630 --> 00:40:58,050
there's something going on
between you two.

866
00:40:58,050 --> 00:41:00,930
You two must have been having
a secret affair.

867
00:41:01,170 --> 00:41:02,880
That's why you broke off the engagement!

868
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:04,610
What nonsense are you talking?

869
00:41:04,640 --> 00:41:05,940
[He's Bakery]

870
00:41:06,040 --> 00:41:06,590
Brother.

871
00:41:10,630 --> 00:41:11,630
Second Brother!

872
00:41:12,150 --> 00:41:13,400
Second Brother, are you alright?

873
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:15,130
I won't let you two get your way!

874
00:41:15,360 --> 00:41:17,860
I still have the marriage contract
left by my parents.

875
00:41:17,860 --> 00:41:19,990
I'm not breaking off this engagement!

876
00:41:20,570 --> 00:41:23,410
He Ketian, I will marry you
no matter what!

877
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:25,670
Zhu Yizhi, keep dreaming!

878
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:26,670
I will never marry

879
00:41:26,670 --> 00:41:28,070
a heartless pig like you!

880
00:41:28,070 --> 00:41:28,530
You!

881
00:42:02,120 --> 00:42:02,830
[He's Bakery]

882
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:09,750
[He's Bakery]

883
00:42:26,700 --> 00:42:31,020
[He's Bakery]

884
00:42:29,770 --> 00:42:30,570
Young Master.

885
00:42:31,150 --> 00:42:31,950
Young Master.

886
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:36,340
If you dare step foot
into He's Bakery again,

887
00:42:36,360 --> 00:42:38,890
I'll make sure you rest at home
for a long time.

888
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:40,250
I won't come anymore.

889
00:42:40,250 --> 00:42:41,450
I won't come anymore.

890
00:42:42,700 --> 00:42:44,930
-I won't come anymore.
-Do you still want money?

891
00:42:44,930 --> 00:42:46,590
No, no.

892
00:42:46,620 --> 00:42:48,270
What about your relationship with Miss He?

893
00:42:48,270 --> 00:42:50,070
I have no relationship with her,

894
00:42:50,090 --> 00:42:51,260
nothing at all.

895
00:42:52,270 --> 00:42:53,010
Scram.

896
00:42:57,830 --> 00:42:59,870
Thank you for your help, Mr. Lu.

897
00:43:00,510 --> 00:43:01,440
It was nothing.

898
00:43:01,550 --> 00:43:02,400
Ketian.

899
00:43:03,010 --> 00:43:03,790
Ke!

900
00:43:03,560 --> 00:43:05,580
[He's Bakery]

901
00:43:05,070 --> 00:43:05,650
Um...

902
00:43:05,710 --> 00:43:06,440
Ke!

903
00:43:06,440 --> 00:43:07,150
What's going on?

904
00:43:07,150 --> 00:43:08,190
Why are there so many people here?

905
00:43:08,190 --> 00:43:09,030
I was scared to death just now.

906
00:43:09,030 --> 00:43:10,970
Do you know?
Zhu Yizhi came to make trouble,

907
00:43:10,970 --> 00:43:12,150
demanding money from me.

908
00:43:12,150 --> 00:43:13,690
How could I possibly give him any money?

909
00:43:13,690 --> 00:43:16,310
Then, that guy started getting violent!

910
00:43:16,330 --> 00:43:17,090
Are you okay?

911
00:43:16,940 --> 00:43:22,270
[He's Bakery]

912
00:43:18,030 --> 00:43:18,320
Chief Lu.

913
00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:19,120
It's nothing.

914
00:43:19,720 --> 00:43:21,380
Thank you for your help today.

915
00:43:22,520 --> 00:43:24,510
Lu Chi, thank you.

916
00:43:25,290 --> 00:43:26,020
My pleasure.

917
00:43:28,440 --> 00:43:30,190
This guy is really something.

918
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:32,230
He truly is able to protect Ke.

919
00:43:36,960 --> 00:43:37,900
Brother Lu.

920
00:43:39,470 --> 00:43:40,720
Thank you so much.

921
00:43:42,060 --> 00:43:42,720
It's nothing.

922
00:43:42,720 --> 00:43:44,010
Are you hurt?

923
00:43:45,240 --> 00:43:46,060
No.

924
00:43:46,300 --> 00:43:47,760
Your hair is all messed up.

925
00:43:48,150 --> 00:43:49,210
It's fine.

926
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:51,920
Are you really okay?

927
00:43:51,920 --> 00:43:52,920
Really, I'm fine.

928
00:43:55,450 --> 00:43:56,530
Let me see.

929
00:43:56,600 --> 00:43:57,370
Look.

930
00:44:00,330 --> 00:44:01,530
I'm glad you're okay.

931
00:44:02,380 --> 00:44:06,050
[He's Bakery]

932
00:44:02,790 --> 00:44:04,560
Second Brother, I've troubled you again.

933
00:44:04,560 --> 00:44:06,360
Not at all. I'll help you.

934
00:44:06,120 --> 00:44:10,300
[Shi's Mansion]

935
00:44:11,550 --> 00:44:13,510
Brother Lu, thank you for today.

936
00:44:13,800 --> 00:44:14,840
If it weren't for you,

937
00:44:14,840 --> 00:44:16,320
I don't know what
would have happened to Ketian.

938
00:44:16,320 --> 00:44:19,150
-Kexian's shop...
-Ke, don't be so polite.

939
00:44:19,390 --> 00:44:20,710
Your family is my family,

940
00:44:20,710 --> 00:44:22,230
your friends are my friends.

941
00:44:22,230 --> 00:44:23,690
That's all part of my duty.

942
00:44:24,870 --> 00:44:26,290
Thank you, Brother Lu.

